Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:25.21,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,映し出す鏡に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:35.19,SongChn,,0000,0000,0000,,幸福一定和悲哀很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:35.19,SongRom,,0000,0000,0000,,{\K80}kit{\K60}to {\K30}shi{\K30}a{\K20}wa{\K20}se {\K200}wa {\K80}{\K60}ka{\K50}na{\K50}shi{\K50}mi {\K30}ni {\K30}ni{\K30}tei{\K90}ru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:35.19,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,きっと幸せは 哀しみに似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:43.23,SongChn,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上心靈的瞳眸
